    • io.dropwizard.views.View

  • Type Parameters:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CitiesView, ErrorView, GraphView, HomeView, LoginView, MyCitiesView, NewCityView, NewPersonView, PersonsView, PersonView, ValidationErrorView
    public abstract class MaterializePage<H extends PagePart,​F extends PagePart>
extends io.dropwizard.views.View
    Abstract class that creates basic HTML page template. This template consist of three parts: Header,Body,Footer.
    This basic template loads CSS and JS files, that are defined in materialize_page.ftl or on runtime by cssFiles,jsFiles lists.
